225
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,593
Marta, hallo.

226
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,672
Ich bin Hector.

227
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,639
Und ich bin Tony.

228
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:57,189
